but his mother still refuses to see you.

31
00:02:41,980 --> 00:02:44,579
Your parents will definitely become furious.

32
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:47,460
That's why

33
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:49,260
I don't know how to tell them.

34
00:02:50,820 --> 00:02:52,350
What about Zhousheng Chen?

35
00:02:53,740 --> 00:02:55,670
We haven't really talked about it.

36
00:02:56,620 --> 00:02:57,480
Let's not talk about this.

37
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,740
I'll cook for you guys.

38
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,110
Good morning, sir.

39
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:10,420
Good morning, sir.

40
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,220
Good morning.

41
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:14,830
-Professor Zhousheng.
-Let's go.

42
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:15,430
Director.

43
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:18,590
Let me make the introductions.

44
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:19,520
He is the person

45
00:03:19,579 --> 00:03:20,660
in charge of our

46
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:21,380
key laboratory,

47
00:03:21,380 --> 00:03:22,910
Professor Zhousheng Chen.

48
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:23,660
This is

49
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,100
Professor Zhang

50
00:03:25,170 --> 00:03:26,460
from Department of Chemistry, Zhenghua University.

51
00:03:26,460 --> 00:03:26,820
Professor Zhang.

52
00:03:26,820 --> 00:03:27,340
Nice to meet you.

53
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:28,600
This is Professor Jin.

54
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:29,540
Professor Jin.

55
00:03:29,540 --> 00:03:30,470
Nice to meet you.

56
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:31,420
By the way,

57
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:33,540
