58
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:34,820
Yes, I remember.

59
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,820
He was a visiting professor.

60
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:39,340
Mr. Zhousheng is young and talented.

61
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:41,900
