78
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:23,140
In fact, these two

79
00:04:23,260 --> 00:04:24,180
have always been

80
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:25,420
in charge of the lab here.

81
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:26,500
I'm already working on

82
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:27,420
a new lab.

83
00:04:28,980 --> 00:04:29,740
Li.

84
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:32,420
It seems that you can't retain talents.

85
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,400
Professor Jin.

86
00:04:34,659 --> 00:04:35,780
No matter what you say,

87
00:04:35,780 --> 00:04:36,740
I've convinced him to

88
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:37,980
set up a lab here.

89
00:04:38,260 --> 00:04:38,860
And you?

90
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:40,300
You didn't even have a chance

91
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:41,230
to convince him.

92
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,140
I can't compete with you

93
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,500
