100
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:59,180
I'm interested in the project they are doing.

101
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:02,020
Besides, my wife likes it there.

102
00:05:03,140 --> 00:05:03,660
This way.

103
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:03,990
Okay.

104
00:05:08,580 --> 00:05:09,910
Everything is the same.

105
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:11,780
Nothing has changed.

106
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:14,300
The last time we met,

107
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,680
